title: Putin Says the USA Is Now the Soviet Union ... Thanks, Joe Biden!
description:
Russian President Vladimir Putin claims America is the new Soviet Union. Thanks to Joe Biden, he has a point. Also, the NBA bends over for China. Again. And do you agree with Stephen Colbert that the Senate is undemocratic?
